<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>The guardrails of data privacy</strong></h2>



<p>The <a href="https://cert.gov.ng/ngcert/resources/Nigeria_Data_Protection_Act_2023.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nigeria Data Protection Act (NDPA) 2023</a><strong> </strong>mandates that data controllers, including fintechs, must secure informed and explicit consent before processing personal data for direct marketing.&nbsp;</p>



